      <title>油价上涨，美国就业数据公布前股市举步维艰：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国关键就业数据公布之前，欧洲股市和美国股指期货艰难上涨，这些数据可能明确利率走势。随着交易员追踪中东敌对行动的升级，油价延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
